We are very excited to offer this new Treatment at the SkinSpa! JET PLASMA allows even more result-driven work that applies to many varied skin concerns.
What is Jet Plasma?
The Plasma is in the form of a gas that goes though the handheld device, interacting with an energized electrode tip to deliver a cooler atmospheric temperature gas that creates no wounding or trauma to the skin, leading to tissue remodeling and repair (collagen stimulation, skin tightening, reducing inflammation and killing surface bacteria)
IMPROVES:
•lines and wrinkles + skin firmness
•acne 
•hyperpigmentation 
•redness 
WHAT’S MORE: 
•zero downtime and no discomfort. 
•even skin conditions like eczema and rosacea are safe and appropriate to treat
•treatments can be days apart (or weekly) for a quicker result.
•treatments can stand alone or be paired with other treatments like chemical peel or LED.
@pro_plasma_esthetic
